The statistical significance of the differences between reported annual CO2 emissions and those derived here (Fig. 2b) are investigated through the use of a single-sample t test, since as with all reported emissions there is only a single reported value for each facility. This analysis tests the null hypothesis that can be stated as: \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
